data.title: Nestea Lipton
data.description: Nestea is a brand of iced tea and cold beverage solutions owned by Nestlé,[1] manufactured by The Coca-Cola Company and distributed by Nestlé's beverage department in the United States and by Beverage Partners Worldwide (BPW)
